title: Counter-Strike 1.6 Escape WarZone 2017
description: ScreenShot: http://cs16-go.ru/_ld/0/35438716.jpg Play one of the most played game in the world , Counter-Strike 1.6 Escape WarZone , now with a lot of modification . The client game kit , works fine , now it works more fastly than others . You'll fell like the pro's of this game . Be the one ! Few things which was added on this version : # A guard which will verify all servers activity [ If one is trying to modify your game client , the guard will block it ] # A list of servers updated weekly ! # Now all your configurations will be saved # New skins for a HIGH FPS and on the worst PC # The client kit works on all multiplayer server [ which have the protocol 47/48 ] # Includes the latest bots # The archive max. size is 250 [ more less then other clients ] To play , just download and extract !
